			Profile
			
			EducationalBackground
&nbsp;
ZhouGuping,borninFebruary1957,wasstudyingintheDepartmentofEducation,HangzhouUniversitybetween1978and1982,andhasbeenworkingintheCollegeofEducation,HangzhouUniversityandthelaterZhejiangUniversitysinceshewasgraduated.ShewasavisitingscholartotheUniversityofWesternAustraliafromOctober1991toOctober1992andavisitingscholarinBritainfromJanuarytoJune2000.
&nbsp;
Teaching
&nbsp;
SheiscurrentlyaprofessoranddoctoralsupervisorwithanorientationinSino-foreigneducationexchanges,highereducationstudiesandschoolmoraleducation.Sheofferscourseslike&ldquo;HistoryofModernChineseEducation&rdquo;tomastercandidates;&ldquo;HistoryofChineseHigherEducation&rdquo;and&ldquo;IntroductionstoEducationalClassics&rdquo;todoctoralcandidates.
&nbsp;
Publications
&nbsp;
Inaddition,shehasundertakenalotofkeyandspecializedprojectsatprovincialandnationallevelsandfromsomegovernmentdepartments,publishedmanypaperswithhighqualityinthenationalpublicationsandwrittenseveralbooksdevotedtoeducation.
&nbsp;
Administrativetasks
&nbsp;
Moreover,sheshouldersmanyadministrativetasks.SheisthestandingdeputydirectorofAcademyofSocialSciences,memberofexpertteamoftheNationalEducationalScientificPlanning,directorofChineseEducationAssociation,standingdirectoranddeputysecretarygeneralofNationalEducationHistoryResearchInstituteanddeputydirectorofZhejiangEducationAssociation,etc.
&nbsp;
Awards
&nbsp;
Shehaswonmanyawardsforbeinganoutstandingprofessorandacapableleader.SheisnowenjoyingthespecialgrantfromtheStateCouncilforherremarkableachievement.
&nbsp;
			
				
